deck_description:
Basic idea is to find a way into making Double Helix and then tutor up Quik-Fix. Then you can proceed to link combo to (ideally) Accesscode Talker and Union Carrier, and then use Union Carrier to equip Accesscode with Dragon Buster. Too many combo variations and end boards to list, but that is the basic concept.

You can try running Dragoon as well but I felt like it wasn't worth having an extra 3 bricks in a deck already with quite a few.

&nbsp;
